txt.en: Minor Emblem of the Uttermost West[e]

The Minor Emblem of the Uttermost West is an item of Power crafted by the Elves of the Second Age. Using this item will grant to you a bonus to Melee, Ranged, and Tactical Defences for a short time as long as you do not move too far from the empowered point.
Minor Emblem of the Uttermost West[p]
